Additional Notice:

The performance evaluation standard values data included in this skill are derived from
《企业绩效评价标准值（2025年版）》published by the Performance Assessment Bureau of 
the State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission (SASAC) of the 
State Council, published by Economic Science Press.

This skill is for reference and analytical purposes only. The standard values data 
belongs to its original publisher. Users should refer to the official publication 
for authoritative data.
